attributes.title: Achievement Haunter: Yorktown Memorial Hospital
attributes.caption: Geoff Ramsey challenges the Achievement Hunter crew to explore a haunted location and draw out the lingering paranormal spirits using fear as their tactic.
attributes.description: Geoff Ramsey challenges the Achievement Hunter crew to explore a haunted location and draw out the lingering paranormal spirits using fear as their tactic. On this episode, the AH crew travels to Yorktown Memorial Hospital to search for evil nuns, a terrifying doctor and a vengeful 8 year old girl.

attributes.title: Shreveport Auditorium/Oakland Cemetery
attributes.caption: The Achievement Haunter crew heads to Shreveport, Louisiana to investigate the ghosts of a philanthropic brothel owner, the victims of a yellow fever epidemic, and the King of Rock and Roll himself, Elvis Presley.
attributes.description: The Achievement Haunter crew heads to Shreveport, Louisiana to investigate the ghosts of a philanthropic brothel owner, the victims of a yellow fever epidemic, and the King of Rock and Roll himself, Elvis Presley.

attributes.title: The Hanging Jail
attributes.caption: The Gothic “Hanging Jail” of Deridder, Louisiana sets the stage for the Achievement Haunter crew to use their unique blend of antagonism and playful pranks to try and draw out the ghosts.
attributes.description: The Gothic “Hanging Jail” of Deridder, Louisiana sets the stage for the Achievement Haunter crew to use their unique blend of antagonism and playful pranks to try and draw out the ghosts of a cruel jailer and two murderers who faced the jail’s infamous gallows.

attributes.title: The Magnolia Hotel
attributes.caption: A historic hotel in Seguin, Texas draws the interest of the Achievement Haunter crew, who hope to make contact with the ghostly guests of the Magnolia.
attributes.description: A historic hotel in Seguin, Texas draws the interest of the Achievement Haunter crew, who hope to make contact with the ghostly guests of the Magnolia, including two children who died under particularly tragic circumstances and a potential murderer.

attributes.title: Long Leaf Sawmill
attributes.caption: In one of the most dangerous haunts yet, the Achievement Haunter crew investigates a defunct sawmill in Long Leaf, Louisiana.
attributes.description: In one of the most dangerous haunts yet, the Achievement Haunter crew investigates a defunct sawmill in Long Leaf, Louisiana. Wile Geoff gets an idea to ratchet up Gavin's fear Jeremy has a ghostly encounter searching for an evil foreman and his victims.

attributes.title: The Hell-Fire Caves
attributes.caption: The ghost-hunting crew of Achievement Haunter journeys all the way to West Wycombe, England, where they investigate the famous “Hell-Fire Caves.”
attributes.description: The ghost-hunting crew of Achievement Haunter journeys all the way to West Wycombe, England, where they investigate the famous “Hell-Fire Caves”, a haunted underground location that holds the secrets of a murdered young woman and a debaucherous secret society.

attributes.title: Pioneer Village
attributes.caption: Deep in the heart of Texas! The Achievement Haunter crew takes a lesson in paranormal history as they venture down the road to Gonzales, Texas, home to the transitive spirits of a flaming ghost, a proud blacksmith, and the ghost of Bruno.
attributes.description: Deep in the heart of Texas! The Achievement Haunter crew takes a lesson in paranormal history as they venture down the road to Gonzales, Texas, home to the transitive spirits of a flaming ghost, a proud blacksmith, and the ghost of Bruno, who tragically died after a horrific accident.

attributes.title: Missouri State Penitentiary
attributes.caption: In the season finale of Achievement Haunter, the crew treks to Jefferson City, Missouri, a place known as the “Bloodiest 47 Acres in America.”
attributes.description: In the season finale of Achievement Haunter, the crew treks to Jefferson City, Missouri, a place known as the “Bloodiest 47 Acres in America.” The team attempts to hunt down the ghosts of death row inmates, hardened criminals, and a snitch killed in one of worst riots in American history.

attributes.title: Season 1 Recap Special
attributes.caption: Full of bonus, never-before-seen footage, deleted scenes and more, the Haunter cast sits down with director and co-creator Daniel Fabelo to discuss this season's most ridiculous moments and review some of their most haunting evidence.
attributes.description: Full of bonus, never-before-seen footage, deleted scenes and more, the Haunter cast sits down with director and co-creator Daniel Fabelo to discuss this season's most ridiculous moments and review some of their most haunting evidence.
